Overview

  The CRX Maven Plugin is responsible for collecting all the resources of a Google Chrome Extension and packaging
  them into a signed CRX archive.

* Goals Overview

  * {{{./crx-mojo.html}crx:crx}} is the default goal invoked during the packaging phase for projects with a packaging
  type of crx. It
  builds
   the signed CRX archive.

